{"id":408,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":10,"title":"10. Telephone call (2)","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":9,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/10-telephone-call.408/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/10-telephone-call-2022-03-07-20-54-21/0-10-telephone-call.mp3","transcript":"Hello, Jack. This is Dave.\nI want to return the book I borrowed from you last night.\nWill you be home at about six o'clock?\nYes, I will. I'll be cooking dinner.\nOh! Well. Then I won't come over at six.\nWhy not?\nI don't want to disturb you.\nDon't worry! You won't disturb me.\nOK. I'll see you at six.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:27","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hello, Jack. This is Dave.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/10-telephone-call-2022-03-07-20-54-21/1.mp3","time_start":2.36,"time_end":4.64},{"position":2,"content":"I want to return the book I borrowed from you last night.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/10-telephone-call-2022-03-07-20-54-21/2.mp3","time_start":4.64,"time_end":7.47},{"position":3,"content":"Will you be home at about six o'clock?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/10-telephone-call-2022-03-07-20-54-21/3.mp3","time_start":7.47,"time_end":9.47},{"position":4,"content":"Yes, I will. I'll be cooking dinner.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/10-telephone-call-2022-03-07-20-54-21/4.mp3","time_start":9.47,"time_end":11.73},{"position":5,"content":"Oh! Well. Then I won't come over at six.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/10-telephone-call-2022-03-07-20-54-21/5.mp3","time_start":11.73,"time_end":14.93},{"position":6,"content":"Why not?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/10-telephone-call-2022-03-07-20-54-21/6.mp3","time_start":14.93,"time_end":15.79},{"position":7,"content":"I don't want to disturb you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/10-telephone-call-2022-03-07-20-54-21/7.mp3","time_start":15.99,"time_end":17.55},{"position":8,"content":"Don't worry! You won't disturb me.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/10-telephone-call-2022-03-07-20-54-21/8.mp3","time_start":17.55,"time_end":19.87},{"position":9,"content":"OK. I'll see you at six.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/10-telephone-call-2022-03-07-20-54-21/9.mp3","time_start":19.87,"time_end":21.93}]}